synopsis: A regular office woman, finds she keeps breaking her computer and other electronic equipment.  A group of men try to get them to come with her (introducing the Foundation), but are stopped by Chinami and her partner Maori, in suits which enhance their powers.

title.jp: All Girl High School Infiltration Misson

synopsis: Chinami and Maori infiltrate a school, which has been bought by the Foundation, where they are found to be testing all the students, for the E power.

The team goes to investigate a school girl who is though to have the E power.. but ends up being her pet bat.  The Foundation arrives to try and subdue it, but when she lets the pet go, they change over to trying to capture Chinami and Maori.
Chinami and Maori travel north to a secret lab, where Kotaro is working on development on their suits.  While there they are attacked by a purple haired man, hired by the Foundation.

title.jp: Go Go West Mission, Part One!

synopsis: Chinami and Maori head to Osaka to protect a E user who emailed OZ.  The E user, Akane, is elusive whenever they try to help her, while being followed by Foundation.  Maori finally is able to get to her, but Akane isn't quite the innocent person in trouble.

title.jp: Go Go West Mission, Part Two!

synopsis: Chinami arrives at the location to fine Maori already gone as well as Akane.  While Chinami goes in search of her, Akane tries to make Maori question who/what she is doing.  Marori eventually escapes, as Chinami finds where she tries to rescue her.

title.jp: Last of the Last of All Missions!
